@Superllama12: I really hope you're joking about using this on [Emrakul](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=193452).  
It's possible to attach this to Emrakul, but you'd have to have a way to get this into play without casting it. Venser, Glimmerpoint Stag and Genesis Wave could work.  
Following which, you now have an Emrakul with the ability "![Tap](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=tap&type=symbol): Sacrifice Emrakul." No extra turn. That comes from hardcasting it.
